features: Strategically placed wind-resistant nylon panels at the hood and front body add durability and keep cold breezes from cutting through. Front panels are lined with soft mesh for comfort

Adjustable, wind-resistant nylon hood adds durability and element protection while a soft knit interiror adds comfort
Rib-knit hem adds comfort and shape retention
2 exterior pockets: front pockets with hidden snap closures are lined with soft knit fabric at knuckle side for comfort
Made with traceable and mulesed free extra-fine Merino wool.
